original_title: An Unauthorized Detailed Account of Gotham 1919 - 1939
overview: Join me as we take a look at the historical and cultural impact a figure like the Batman would have if he had existed in the United States of America from 1919-1939. You'll see various familiar faces as we delve into Gotham's streets and experience it in a way you never have before. Join me in the history of Gotham City. Based on the book by GIANTPANDAKING.
title: An Unauthorized Detailed Account of Gotham 1919 - 1939
